== Chef Add Recipe to Run List
Adds a recipe to a run list for a specific Node in Chef

=== Parameters
  [Recipe Name]
    Name of recipe you wish to add to a run list for a specific node.
  [Node Name]
    Name of node where the run list exists.

=== Sample Configuration
Recipe Name:         my_recipe
Node Name:           test-node

=== Results
[node_json]
  The JSON Object of the modified Node


=== Detailed Description
  This handler adds a recipe to a run list for a particular node 
  in Chef.  If handler is successful, you will receive a JSON response
  as a return with the nodes information, including the run list
  array.
